1.30	Always_(Atlantic_Starr_song)	Always (Atlantic Starr song)	"Always" was the second single from All in the Name of Love, the seventh album from R&amp;B group, Atlantic Starr. The song went to number one on both the Hot Black Singles and Billboard Hot 100 charts in June 1987. The song also spent two weeks atop the U.S. adult contemporary chart. In July, it also topped the Canadian RPM 100 national singles chart, where it remained for two weeks.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/8/86/Atlantic_Starr-Always.jpg/220px-Atlantic_Starr-Always.jpg
